I have completed the initial sections of the PRD document, including the project name, language, original requirements, product goals, and user stories. The next step is to conduct a competitive analysis to identify similar products and their pros and cons.

Since the previous attempt to use the SearchEnhancedQA tool was unsuccessful, I will now proceed to gather information using the browser tool to search for competitive products related to image analysis software that utilizes AI/ML techniques.

I will start by searching for the first keyword: "image analysis software AI ML techniques 2025."

Here’s the command to initiate the search using the browser tool.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Browser.goto",
        "args": {"url": "https://www.google.com/search?q=image+analysis+software+AI+ML+techniques+2025"}
    }
]
```

Since I encountered issues with the browser tool and the SearchEnhancedQA tool is not available, I will proceed with a different approach to gather competitive analysis information. 

I will now use the SearchEnhancedQA tool to search for the second keyword: "personalized recommendation systems for images 2025." This will help me gather insights on competitive products related to personalized recommendations in image analysis.

Here’s the command to initiate the search using the SearchEnhancedQA tool.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "SearchEnhancedQA.run",
        "args": {"query": "personalized recommendation systems for images 2025"}
    }
]
```

